## Third-Party Licenses

This project builds container images using packages from the following sources.
Each package retains its original license:

### Wolfi Packages (https://github.com/wolfi-dev)
Wolfi packages are licensed under various open-source licenses. Each package's
license is listed in its SBOM. Common licenses include:
- Apache-2.0
- MIT
- GPL-2.0-or-later
- LGPL-2.1-or-later
- BSD-3-Clause

### Build Tools
- **apko** (https://github.com/chainguard-dev/apko) - Apache-2.0
- **melange** (https://github.com/chainguard-dev/melange) - Apache-2.0
- **cosign** (https://github.com/sigstore/cosign) - Apache-2.0
- **Trivy** (https://github.com/aquasecurity/trivy) - Apache-2.0

### Package-Specific Licenses
To view the licenses of all packages in a specific image, use:

```bash
# Download and view SBOM
cosign download sbom ghcr.io/rtvkiz/minimal-python:latest | jq '.packages[].licenseConcluded'
```

Or view the image's SBOM via the GitHub Container Registry UI.
